dc_title_s: Detail map of the Upper Mississippi River from Minneapolis, Minnesota to Lake Itasca, v.2
dc_description_s: Survey of the Mississippi River; made under the direction of the Mississippi River Commission. Contains Charts 241-278. Each chart is at a scale of 1:10,000. Charts also show river depths and include an Authorities and Notes section. Some charts show land owners adjacent to the river.||63 x 101 centimeters|Scale 1:20,000.; Scale 1:10,000
